
@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Velvett Holidays";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<section class="section header-section dark">
    <div class="overlay"><img class="property-cover" src="~/Images/bg1.jpg" /></div>
    <div class="container clearfix">
        <div class="col-lg-6 centered aligncenter">
            <div class="centralizing-wrapper">
                <div class="centralized-content">
                    <h1>Don't just visit. <span style="color:#f06eaa">Belong.</span></h1>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<section class="section2 bordered">
    <div class="container clearfix">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12">
                <h2>Velvett Holidays</h2>
                <div class="head-underline-s"> </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12">

                <p>We at Velvett Homestays are here to make every travel of yours as experiential as possible. We are not just building a Homestay portal, we are building a community of like-minded travellers.</p>
                <p>
                    We comprise of travellers who love to travel not just as a hobby or a leisure activity, we travel as it is what drives us. We travel to live as a local. There is also a keen affiliation towards responsible and sustainable living.
                    We might be Homestay specialists in just two regions, but believe this drive to travel can be the key contributing fuel to any journey you wish to make.
                </p>
                <p><br></p>

                <h4>Travel Enquiry Form</h4>
                <div class="head-underline-s"> </div>
                <p>
                    Take a moment to fill out the little attached form and give us a few days to get back to you with travel ideas and tips for any part of our planet.
                </p>
                <p><br></p>

                <h4>Travel Hacks</h4>
                <div class="head-underline-s"> </div>
                <p>
                    Who doesn’t love a travel hack? We have a long list that could serve as a great guide for your next travel.
                </p>
                <p><br></p>
                <h4>Travel Beats</h4>
                <div class="head-underline-s"> </div>
                <p>
                    Visit our You Tube channel, Travel Beats, to see some short but simple videos on many travel destinations.
                </p>
                <p><br></p>
                <h4>Our Travel Ambassadors</h4>
                <div class="head-underline-s"> </div>
                <p>
                    Lastly, don't miss out on what our Travel Ambassadors’ whereabouts. These are people who like us, travel to become locals and want to gladly share some of their best experiences with you.
                    Rest assured you can travel doubt free to some of the places they have scouted and are waiting for you to be explored some more.
                </p>
                <p><br></p>
                <p><br></p>
                <p class="text-right">
                    Your Travelogists
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>